data.description: Great opportunity on this move in ready Home. Previously remodeled and maintained. Plenty of natural light in the living area from the west exposure. Newer Flooring, Kitchen, Bath. Good size Master Bed with a huge walk-in closet.  Spacious Balcony. Lots of Storage Space. Walking distance to the Future Light Rail, Shopping, Transit Center. Minutes away from the main Highway/ Freeways. Here is your Chance. Welcome Home!
